Package: jotdown
Version: 0.1.2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6, libgtk-3-0, libglib2.0-0
Maintainer: Tim Apple <tim@example.com>
Description: A simple, secure note-taking application
 jotDown is a modern note-taking application with encryption,
 search capabilities, and both desktop and command-line interfaces.
 Features include markdown support, theme customization, and
 secure password-based encryption for sensitive notes.
